### GET announcements without query params
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements

### GET announcements with search
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements?search=ноутбук

### GET announcements with sort and page
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements?sort=oldest&page=2

### GET announcement by id (existing)
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements/1

### GET announcement by id (non-existing)
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements/9999

### Create announcement with valid data
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам ноутбук ASUS",
  "description": "Відмінний стан, 16GB RAM, SSD 512GB",
  "price": 18000,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "0991234567"
}

### Create announcement with invalid data
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ноут",
  "description": "Коротко",
  "price": -100,
  "category": "unknown",
  "contactInfo": "123"
}

### Patch announcement with partial data
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 17000,
  "contactInfo": "0997654321"
}

### Patch announcement with non-existing id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 20000
}

### Delete announcement by id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/1

### Delete announcement with non-existing id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/9999
